  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients with a diagnosis of a degenerative condition of the lumbar spine
             undergoing posterior lumbar spinal surgery at Sunnybrook and Women's College Health
             Sciences Centre

          -  Patients who have had previous lumbar surgery

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Traumatic or neoplastic surgical conditions of the lumbar spine
      </textblock>
